org.agmip.util
Class MapUtil

java.lang.Object
  org.agmip.util.MapUtil

public class MapUtil
extends Object

This class provides a simple interface to handle AgMIP bucket entries inside a nested structure. These entries are returned by the AgMIP translators and reflect collections of data (such as weather stations and data, soil information, or field experiment parameters. All methods provided by this class are static

0.15
